[guruh berdentum]

34:42.875 --> 34:45.083
-[bunyi berdentum perlahan]
-[menghidu]

34:45.166 --> 34:47.625
[muzik ngeri dibina perlahan-lahan]

34:51.916 --> 34:53.250
-Papa?
